Title: Alexander McQueen
Body (HTML): The restrictions of 2020 meant that with a lack of resources, Alexander McQueen decided to create a collection made predominantly of upcycled overstock fabrics. This T-shirt, for example, is crafted from cotton and features patch logo taping which is cut from the selvedge for a clean finish. Wear it with everything from off-duty sweatpants to tailored trousers to showcase the label’s sustainable practices.

Title: Alexander McQueen
Body (HTML): Alexander McQueen’s Spring/Summer 2022 collection was inspired by the sky and, more broadly, the beauty of nature as a whole. While you may expect this theme to carry motifs of sunshine and butterflies, the label opts to approach it via its typical gothic lens, depicting ominous – but nonetheless magnificent – grey-tinted clouds across pieces like these swim shorts.

Title: Zegna
Body (HTML): By applying its knowledge of sophisticated tailoring to the world of athleisure, Ermenegildo Zegna creates must-have pieces for the modern man – this jacket included. The lightweight design is imagined with cuffed sleeves and a high neckline for added warmth – while the more casual fit gives this versatile piece multiple outfit options within your wardrobe.

Title: Zegna
Body (HTML): Z Zegna eschews cotton when crafting this T-shirt, such is its preference for high-performance materials that can keep up with the modern gentleman’s active lifestyle. Its alternative? Techmerino wool jersey – an innovative material created by the brand and prized for its ultra-soft texture, breathable warmth and effortless heat regulation.How to wear Harrods: Style with a jacket, shorts, sneakers and a backpack.

Title: Zegna
Body (HTML): Ermenegildo Zegna creates versatile basics from high-quality materials, so you’ll get plenty of wear from each one. These trousers are constructed from a cotton-stretch fabric with just the right amount of give. They’re shaped to a flattering slim-leg profile and have pressed creases through the front for extra shape and a tailored finish.

Title: Burberry
Body (HTML):
A dependable logo sweater is a must-have addition to any gentleman’s essential edit, and this offering from Burberry ticks all the right boxes. Crafted from a sublimely soft Italian-woven wool blend, it's intarsia-knitted with the label’s instantly recognisable logo styled in bold, contrast lettering.
 How to wear Harrods: Style with shorts, sneakers and a belt bag.
